milestones.description: Tendulkar and Rahul Dravid's 331-run partnership is IND's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 318 between Ganguly and Rahul Dravid
Tendulkar's 186 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for IND), surpassing Ganguly's 183
Tendulkar and Rahul Dravid's 331-run partnership is the highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 318 between Ganguly and Rahul Dravid
India's 175-run win against New Zealand is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 157-run win against Sri Lanka
Tendulkar and Rahul Dravid's 331-run partnership is IND's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 318 between Rahul Dravid and Ganguly

stories.title: Tendulkar overhauls Azharuddin's record tally of runs in one-day Internationals
stories.summary: Little master Sachin Tendulkar became the leading run scorer in the one-day internationals during his innings of 69 against New Zealand at Nairobi Gymkhana in the final of ICC Knock Out

stories.title: India get their own back with interest
stories.summary:
After the beating India took at Rajkot, I think the Indian team said
whatever you can do we can do better
